        "TileImage": "$($repository 74c99b73-3d45-4c37-b68c-600022714d43).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47. Our client has issued a contract on five seemingly random people scattered across Marrakesh. In truth, these five people appear to be linked to the ransoming of 5-year-old Daisy Burnam in Ontario, Canada nine years ago. Although her millionaire parents paid the ransom, Daisy&apos;s corpse was found five weeks later. Our client wants this handled as silently and as quickly as possible, despite the targets&apos; locations. I&apos;m sure that won&apos;t be a problem for you, though, 47. Good luck.",
